@absence_tracker_HostAddress = http://localhost:5015

### Register a new user
POST {{absence_tracker_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Login and store JWT token
# @name login
POST {{absence_tracker_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Get user profile (protected route using JWT token)
GET {{absence_tracker_HostAddress}}/api/auth/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Refresh token (protected route)
POST {{absence_tracker_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Create a new course (protected route)
POST {{absence_tracker_HostAddress}}/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "name": "Mathematics 101",
  "description": "Introduction to Mathematics - Basic concepts and fundamentals"
}
